{
  "stem": "4122.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we were in-- at home in Zawalow, and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] when the Germans came in, we had-- they took all those people to work.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the first day, when they just came, they started to ask where the Jewish people lived.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Gentiles, the Polish people who were there, they right away brought them into the Jewish places where they were.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were very happy to see them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They-- when they came in, they were happy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They screamed, [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Hora ?], [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Hora ?], to see them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they showed right away the Jewish places.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They start taking us to work, to all kind of work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I had three houses away from us, a friend who went to school together with me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he joined the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Romich. ?] [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He joined the Nazis a little later.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he was pro them right away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he, he took my father to work, and other people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They cut off their beards.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they, they took them to, to ditch, like street work, to do all kinds of dirty works.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They took them, like when it was lot rain or mud, they had to lay down, put them on the floor, and get up, lay down, and get up, just to humiliate them.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They shall be-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] and beaten.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they took them to dig stones.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We have-- like our city was-- now I go back to this, how the city was.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They had-- it was surrounded like with-- it was in a, in a vale, or around was hills.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The hills had stones.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we had to go dig those stones.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They took the men specially.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they beat them.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
